--- title: "A3: Pocket Money" author: "Tanya Michelle Justin" --- ## **Guys have more pocket money than Gals.** ### What are we trying to find out? The aim of this experiment is to determine whether there is a significant difference in pocket money between males and females. ### How was the data collected? The sample data for this study was collected from students at MAHE who were available at the time of data gathering. To minimize selection bias, participants were chosen through a coin toss, which determined whether each student would participate in the survey. This sample aims to represent the entire MAHE student population. This data was gathered from 60 individuals 30 males and 30 females . Each student was asked about the amount of money spent the day before. ::: {.cell} ```{.r .cell-code} library(mosaic) ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stderr} ``` Registered S3 method overwritten by 'mosaic': method from fortify.SpatialPolygonsDataFrame ggplot2 ``` ::: ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stderr} ``` The 'mosaic' package masks several functions from core packages in order to add additional features.
